Description:
This app lets you check real-time weather for any city using the OpenWeatherMap API. You can also log daily weather entries and track them over time in a local file.

Features:

Enter city name to get current temperature and weather conditions

Uses OpenWeatherMap API to fetch live data

Allows you to write daily weather notes (like a journal)

Stores all entries in a local file (weather_log.txt)

Simple GUI built with Tkinter

Note: 
    You need to have an API key to run the code which you can get from https://openweathermap.org/api